comments.body:
@PaulHigin Could you please look the issue?

I tried follow with strange behavior:
```powershell
0..0 | ForEach-Object -Parallel {
	$Host.UI.SupportsVirtualTerminal
}
```
```powershell
function qqq {
[CmdletBinding()]
param()
	$Host.UI.SupportsVirtualTerminal
}

0..0 | ForEach-Object -Parallel {
    qqq
}
```

```powershell
0..0 | ForEach-Object -Parallel {
function qqq {
[CmdletBinding()]
param()
	$Host.UI.SupportsVirtualTerminal
}
	qqq
}
```
